reviews.headline: Good when it works, very drying
reviews.comments:
I have very stubborn straight east asian eyelashes and this mascara can hold a curl. I would not really say it's that volumizing, but it definitely helped hold my lashes in the shape I wanted which most mascaras I've tried cannot do. It looks very nice on my lashes, and I have not experienced smudging. 

The formula is very drying for your lashes, so I don't use it every day. The tube itself also dries out quickly, faster than I could use it, and I do not pump my mascara wand. If I were to buy again, I would get the mini/travel size. For the price of the full tube I would not buy again because even though I liked the results I got, there was a lot of unusable product in the tube.

reviews.headline: Waterproof but it smudges?
reviews.comments: I loved this mascara at first, it always looked so pretty right after. I would put it on before work or a night out, i would notice after a few hours the under of my eyes would smudge. Makes me sad bc I like the wand and lancome but i dont think its worth keeping. 2/5 stars

faceoff_positive.comments:
I'm so glad I got to give this Lancôme lash mascara a try.. what I like about it is the brush and the formula, I like that this is not a waterproof mascara, however it performs like a waterproof mascara, what I mean by that is that it actually.. stays on without getting raccoon eyes.. stays on all day long. 
Doesn't flake off throughout the day.
Does make my lashes look longer and fuller.. I find that the wand is easy peasy to use, It is buildable without making it clumpy looking... No problem removing it at night. 
The application wand make my lashes stay curled... The black color is black enough to cover your lashes and look amazing... overall I was very impressed with this mascara. I wouldn't hesitate to buy again. Good job on this mascara Pr gifted.
faceoff_positive.headline: fabulous

faceoff_negative.comments: I absolutely LOVE this mascara, but the bottle has a little round piece, that you pull the brush through, that comes off 100% of the time within about 2 weeks of starting to use it. Then the mascara starts to clump and dry up. However, I find myself buying it even though I know this will happen because it's the best mascara I have ever found… until it's not. I just wish it would last longer than a few weeks.
faceoff_negative.headline: Best mascara ever… until it's not
